
%html.no-js
  %head
    %meta{charset: "utf-8"}/
    %meta{content: "IE=edge,chrome=1", "http-equiv" => "X-UA-Compatible"}/
    %title Showcase - Landing Page
    %meta{content: "", name: "description"}/
    %meta{content: "width=device-width", name: "viewport"}/
    %link{href: "css/bootstrap.min.css", rel: "stylesheet"}/
    %link{href: "css/onepage-scroll.css", rel: "stylesheet"}/
    %link{href: "css/main.css", rel: "stylesheet"}/
    /[if lte IE 9]
      <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/ie9-and-down.css" />
    %link{href: "/favicon.ico", rel: "icon", type: "image/x-icon"}/
    %script{src: "js/vendor/modernizr-2.6.2-respond-1.1.0.min.js"}
  %body
    .main
      %section.home
        .container
          .home-phone.hide.hidden-xs.col-xs-12.col-sm-5
            %img.iphone-3{alt: "", src: "img/iphone-3.png"}/
          .row
            .home-copy.col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2.animated.fadeInDown.delay-2
              %h1.demo1
                We love
                %br/
                %span.rotate Imagination, Technology, Creativity, Innovation, Big Dreams
              %p We've been hard at work hand crafting amazing products for your team. We would like to share our recent work, hope you like it.
              %span.take-a-look.animated.fadeInDown.delay-8
                %i.entypo-down-open>
                Take a look
      %section.slide-1.slide.full-color
        .container
          .row
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.iphone-container
              %img.hide.iphone-1{alt: "", src: "img/iphone-1.png"}/
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.copy
              %h2.hide.slide-1-title.slide-titles Finally it's Launch day
              %p.slide-1-1.hide
                Use showcase to present your latest work in an elgantly simple way. Present multiple screenshots with copy to keep things flowing.
              %p.slide-1-2.hide.hidden-xs
                You can easily add more slides and change the animation speed, style.
              %p.slide-1-3.hide.hidden-xs
                Mix it up and use the background image, flat colours or even big video.
              %i.hide.entypo-down-open.slide-1-scroll.scroll-down
      %section.slide-2.slide.full-color
        .container
          .row
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.copy
              %h2.hide.slide-2-title.slide-titles Simple is effective
              %p.slide-2-1.hide
                Use the three example layouts to take your users on a journey through your app. Use bootsraps grid system to control copy/phone size.
              %p.slide-2-2.hide.hidden-xs
                Simply slide between slides just likes Apple's latest series of promotion sites.
              %p.slide-2-3.hide.hidden-xs
                Remember simplicty will keep your work looking its best. Keep it simple.
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.iphone-container
              %img.hide.iphone-2{alt: "", src: "img/iphone-2.png"}/
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.copy
              %p.slide-2-4.hide.hidden-xs
                Use the settings cog to see what options you have avalible. Perhaps have a big video of your team hard at work in the office.
              %p.slide-2-5.hide.hidden-xs
                Adding animations is easy, simply follow the examples in the code.
              %p.slide-2-6.hide.hidden-xs
                Changing slide colors, images and video is all really easy.
              %i.hide.entypo-down-open.slide-2-scroll.scroll-down.hidden-xs
      %section.slide-3.slide.full-color
        .container
          .row
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.copy
              %h2.hide.slide-3-title.slide-titles Obvisouly its Responsive
              %p.slide-3-1.hide
                Works great all all screen sizes. Use bootstraps default classes hidden-xs hidden-sm to control what you see.
              %p.slide-3-2.hide.hidden-xs
                Show only the top half of the phone or hide it all together on mobile.
              %p.slide-3-3.hide.hidden-xs
                PSD files are added for your screenshots, drop them right in and be up and running quickly.
              %i.hide.entypo-down-open.slide-3-scroll.scroll-down.hidden-xs
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.iphone-container
              %img.hide.iphone-3{alt: "", src: "img/iphone-3.png"}/
      %section.contact.full-color
        .row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3.col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
            %h2 Keep in touch
            %p We're always keen to here what you think, send us a message from all the usual places. Don't forget to sign up for our newsletter.
            .newsletter.clearfix
              %form{role: "form"}
                .form-group
                  %input#emailSignup{name: "signup", placeholder: "Your Email", type: "text"}/
                  %button.btn.btn-signup{type: "submit"}
                    %i.entypo-mail
            .social.clearfix
              %a.social-item.facebook{href: "#"}
                %i.entypo-facebook
              %a.social-item.twitter{href: "#"}
                %i.entypo-twitter
    / /main
    .icon.animated.fadeInLeft.delay-3
      %span Showcase
    .settings.animated.fadeInLeft.delay-4
      %span.settings-icon
        %i.entypo-cog
      %h3.settings-title Settings
      %span.settings-subtitle Home
      %span.toggle-video.hidden-xs toggle video
      %span.toggle-phone.hidden-xs toggle phone
      %span.toggle-opacity-first toggle opacity first
      %span.settings-subtitle Global
      %span.toggle-opacity-all toggle opacity all
      %span.toggle-slide-fade toggle color fade on slide
    %script{src: "//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.10.1/jquery.min.js"}
    :javascript
      window.jQuery || document.write('<script src="js/vendor/jquery-1.10.1.min.js"><\/script>')
    %script{src: "js/vendor/bootstrap.min.js"}
    %script{src: "js/vendor/jquery-ui-1.8.22.custom.min.js"}
    %script{src: "js/vendor/jquery.imagesloaded.min.js"}
    %script{src: "http://vjs.zencdn.net/4.0/video.js"}
    %script{src: "js/vendor/bigvideo.js"}
    %script{src: "js/vendor/jquery.simple-text-rotator.min.js"}
    %script{src: "js/vendor/jquery.onepage-scroll.min.js"}
    %script{src: "js/main.js"}